OL,3,CLocal Elections 2026: ITV News London
OL,4,Cresults hub
OL,6,FLocal elections are taking place in
OL,7,Feach of London's 32 boroughs as well
OL,8,Fas six directly elected mayors in
OL,9,FLondon and Hertfordshire. There are
OL,10,Falso elections in unitary authorities,
OL,11,Fcounty councils and district councils.
OL,13,FThis page will update live as the
OL,14,Fresults are declared.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
